🔹 Q2) Write a cursor to display the names of items whose rate is more than 500.


---

✅ Cursor

DO $$
DECLARE
    rec RECORD;
BEGIN
    FOR rec IN
        SELECT i.itemname
        FROM item i
        JOIN item_supplier isup ON i.itemno = isup.itemno
        WHERE isup.rate > 500
    LOOP
        RAISE NOTICE 'Item: %', rec.itemname;
    END LOOP;
END;
$$;


