🔹 Procedure Question

❓ Write a procedure to accept three numbers and find the maximum number from it.


---

✅ Procedure

CREATE OR REPLACE PROCEDURE max_three(a INT, b INT, c INT)
LANGUAGE plpgsql
AS $$
DECLARE
    max_val INT;
BEGIN
    max_val := a;

    IF b > max_val THEN
        max_val := b;
    END IF;

    IF c > max_val THEN
        max_val := c;
    END IF;

    RAISE NOTICE 'Maximum = %', max_val;
END;
$$;


